title: Project 2
text:
In this project, the goal is to create some interesting and interactive visualizations for analysis of international air travel in the United States.


Monthly data about international air travel in all of the United States from 1990 to 2023:


Rows: 766,693
Columns: 16

title: Examining International Air Travel Within the United States
text: This project was developed by Omar Youssif. For MATH/STAT241 at Reed College. The data is sourced from the U.S. Department of Transportation (data owner: Randall Keizer at randall.keizer@dot.gov) and is accessible through this link.
